{"tid":2046755,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有糭黃店屈桔梗食人血","createTime":"2020-06-01T15:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T15:29:14.000Z","uid":176586,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9811e3e7e640395b8dd9054038db8a5ed44656","tid":2046755,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"#説好的黃圈不分化呢<br />\n#報告黃衛兵<br />\n#捉到一個分化撚<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記得我之前婊過屎家軍B隊桔梗➡️ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/869670276872220/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F869670276872220%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8wZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=639a116e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/869670276872220/</a><br />\n<br />\n前幾日就收到呢個自稱黃店東主嘅Dai Tom嘅報料，話桔梗要賣月餅，仲插到桔梗一頸血，話桔梗抄「和你包」、又插產地、又話好鬼，根住又插桔梗賣洗手液俾黃店食水深。月餅單嘢我都諗住留意吓睇定啲先，但洗手液呢單嘢我就覺得無可厚非。批發市場嘅交易，你自己都係一個商人，唔係無知巿民，市場上好多同類型產品可以比較，你可以話佢食水深，但你唔可以話佢人血，唔係乜撚貴嘅嘢都係叫人血㗎大佬。呢個Dai Tom俾我嘅感覺，就係好想煽動我去做鳩桔梗。<br />\n<br />\n然後佢話峰一轉，屌埋幫手足供應私家飯嘅潮食閣，話懷疑佢同桔梗有利益輸送。然後響錄音當中佢就講話覺得桔梗捐款俾潮食閣好奇怪，仲話「會唔會係潮食閣同桔梗傾好數，講就講係捐20%俾佢哋，但潮食閣回返10%俾桔梗呢？會唔會有咁嘅可能性呢？」。<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度，我就膠都費事俾，冇再回覆佢了。我憎桔梗還憎桔梗，但都唔會無矢放的嘅。呢個Dai Tom嘅報料完全冇任何根據、證據，全部都係佢自己嘅感受同揣測。當時我都冇特別留意，以為佢可能只係一間疑心比較重嘅黃店。但當我今朝發現，原來呢個Dai Tom就係茶一老闆戴仁傑Thomas Dai，咁一切謎底就解開了。佢一開始根本就唔係嚟爆料，而係想借刀殺人。茶一攪「和你包」賺個返尋味，已經諗緊要搞「和你秋」賣月餅，所以當佢發現桔梗搶閘，打算用同一個模式賣月餅嗰陣，出名小氣嘅佢，當然要諗方法剷除競爭對手。有乜方便得過嚟一招借刀殺人？自己賣糭嗰陣就大叫不分化不篤灰，見到人哋賣月餅就即刻分化兼篤灰，仲老屈潮食閣回佣俾人？嗱，茶一戴仁傑呢啲就真係純正分化撚啦！<br />\n<br />\n在此奉勸想嚟同我報料嘅各位，我一向都係好小心咁保護每一個報料人，未經報料人嘅同意，公開報料人身份。但如果有任何人，其身不正立心不良，想利用人西谷剷除異己，陷害無辜之人，咁就等住引火自焚啦。<br />\n<br />\n茶一話要做第二間龍門 ➡️ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875220889650492/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F875220889650492%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8wZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=3625e72c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875220889650492/</a><br />\n<br />\n小黃店報料➡️ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875694209603160/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F875694209603160%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8wZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=d5d17335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875694209603160/</a><br />\n<br />\n茶一黑歷史➡️ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875615716277676/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F875615716277676%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8wZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=4cff13cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875615716277676/</a><br />\n<br />\n#無辜嘅係潮食閣<br />\n#桔梗都係仆街嚟嘅<br />\n#跟美心用暴利價賣月餅<br />\n#自己做茶一個位食大餅<br />\n#小黃店門就食餅碎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875859592919955/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F875859592919955%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8wZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=e9c65dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/875859592919955/</a>"},{"pid":"c925a3a1e6dae692924cc70c5954cff085f0d35c","tid":2046755,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6193791441f1bc9e0875d9982e85abc69971ba0f","tid":2046755,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c55edb7743bec649b842609de0f19f83d1de9227","tid":2046755,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d35dfc79bdb3dd51b97e05f92524117dbb912f72","tid":2046755,"uid":212953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲，但我都要食飯架，無辦法啦"},{"pid":"b9d170b5b6b820ac97d0a2d52fd34c072542bb1c","tid":2046755,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3564e39b58deebc452be2204018e20bb5933592","tid":2046755,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75557027a748d12a1998b3bd5f2a61434ec87c86","tid":2046755,"uid":129335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"但我買左和你包，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6d040cbda71e3dc008698ff8240239e75c0ffd","tid":2046755,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75557027a748d12a1998b3bd5f2a61434ec87c86","tid":2046755,"uid":129335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"但我買左和你包，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"冇辦法 都要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe793dba3cb392ed0e05ebfd22e845e3f777e73","tid":2046755,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"信蕭生啦   蕭生黃到返唔到香港<br />\n<br />\n唔會呃人掛"}]}